COMPLIANCE:
Scene ID: SC_001_001
Allowed events: Artie vs vending machine, dollar bill rejection, chip coil failure, use of aggressive_vending_machine_shaking skill, electrocution, death.
Forbidden milestones: THREAD_CRIT_EXPLOIT (not yet active), CHAR_FIZZ (not yet present), THREAD_THE_ASCENSION (not yet active).

